{"tid":112382,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"深深體會到香港人欠缺笑容","createTime":"2017-02-08T06:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T05:20:23.000Z","uid":83380,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d3c3381149c9744c61da5dd6738c7d13b571718","tid":112382,"uid":83380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/08/135534_aca18ccbe1b82e7c83671c73d3305f20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F08%2F135534_aca18ccbe1b82e7c83671c73d3305f20.jpg&h=824a535f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n 之前睇到呢個post都唔覺得香港人係咁。<br />\n但我做左part time之後覺得呢個報到好中肯<br />\n<br />\n話說本人現正享受大學生活(i大)，因家境貧困所以我去左某醫院做兼職，推下病床，送下文件。<br />\n而工作時候好多時要同d護士or藥劑師接觸，護士都冇乜野大多都好有禮貌。藥劑師最仆街問佢野又好似阻住佢咁黑口黑面，你估我好想下下成個87咁問咁多野咩，上面規定左。<br />\n<br />\n但佢地又十問9唔應，應又應埋d廢話。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如有一日我問師傅有冇a10 xxx份藥(一定要問佢地攞)，之後條仆街黑口黑面咁答我有就有冇就冇嫁啦好點知。<br />\n<br />\nso我覺得香港人真係冇乜笑容<br />\n<br />\n想發洩下，不喜勿插"},{"pid":"548de79ab32f69713628453c8b97ee7c541afd2c","tid":112382,"uid":4346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"因為生活係香港真係笑唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09dffe00f20a7283093288923188be904d08de93","tid":112382,"uid":79056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:15:05.000Z","msg":"望住你笑既都係有陰謀架"},{"pid":"873749c6e610010b1359995a26ebf6c76336df22","tid":112382,"uid":623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:16:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/08/135534_aca18ccbe1b82e7c83671c73d3305f20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F08%2F135534_aca18ccbe1b82e7c83671c73d3305f20.jpg&h=824a535f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n 之前睇到呢個post都唔覺得香港人係咁。<br />\n但我做左part time之後覺得呢個報到好中肯<br />\n<br />\n話說本人現正享受大學生活(i大)，因家境貧困所以我去左某醫院做兼職，推下病床，送下文件。<br />\n而工作時候好多時要同d護士or藥劑師接觸，護士都冇乜野大多都好有禮貌。藥劑師最仆街問佢野又好似阻住佢咁黑口黑面，你估我好想下下成個87咁問咁多野咩，上面規定左。<br />\n<br />\n但佢地又十問9唔應，應又應埋d廢話。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如有一日我問師傅有冇a10 xxx份藥(一定要問佢地攞)，之後條仆街黑口黑面咁答我有就有冇就冇嫁啦好點知。<br />\n<br />\nso我覺得香港人真係冇乜笑容<br />\n<br />\n想發洩下，不喜勿插</blockquote><br />\n人地藥劑師你叫人師傅緊係黑你面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579a13944298ba1bbfee4eca7985ee96b051804b","tid":112382,"uid":8498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:21:56.000Z","msg":"麥記嘅免費笑容都冇咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0287f0f30d64a7c670d3fd6a7aa6a7154850aea8","tid":112382,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:24:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>麥記嘅免費笑容都冇咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n西面mk妹先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2f2bc3d7f1e29020dfb9a51fa4901bc2b9d70c","tid":112382,"uid":83380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:25:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>望住你笑既都係有陰謀架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔笑都到少俾d禮貌，又唔係我想咁多野問佢係上面規定送藥一定要問佢攞"},{"pid":"76b93ec81c986dd016b02261d31005238ca78a7e","tid":112382,"uid":83380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/08/135534_aca18ccbe1b82e7c83671c73d3305f20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F08%2F135534_aca18ccbe1b82e7c83671c73d3305f20.jpg&h=824a535f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n 之前睇到呢個post都唔覺得香港人係咁。<br />\n但我做左part time之後覺得呢個報到好中肯<br />\n<br />\n話說本人現正享受大學生活(i大)，因家境貧困所以我去左某醫院做兼職，推下病床，送下文件。<br />\n而工作時候好多時要同d護士or藥劑師接觸，護士都冇乜野大多都好有禮貌。藥劑師最仆街問佢野又好似阻住佢咁黑口黑面，你估我好想下下成個87咁問咁多野咩，上面規定左。<br />\n<br />\n但佢地又十問9唔應，應又應埋d廢話。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如有一日我問師傅有冇a10 xxx份藥(一定要問佢地攞)，之後條仆街黑口黑面咁答我有就有冇就冇嫁啦好點知。<br />\n<br />\nso我覺得香港人真係冇乜笑容<br />\n<br />\n想發洩下，不喜勿插</blockquote><br />\n人地藥劑師你叫人師傅緊係黑你面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問該如果稱呼？"},{"pid":"492a98d2851ec68ca2c53f8e4d70fd05ed8a1c1e","tid":112382,"uid":79056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:30:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>望住你笑既都係有陰謀架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔笑都到少俾d禮貌，又唔係我想咁多野問佢係上面規定送藥一定要問佢攞</blockquote><br />\n唔笑又唔代表無禮貌<br />\n你又諗下上面規定要問，佢返咁耐工聽過幾多次？"},{"pid":"6a82a828cee07c50a9cb584c6ab54a2e61b422d4","tid":112382,"uid":17619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9d1800dfcc27bb7f2a07e334da01777796b1ad","tid":112382,"uid":42009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:42:32.000Z","msg":"全部都西口西面"},{"pid":"7645ac21d123c455dcef7ced37ea4412965c5195","tid":112382,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:43:13.000Z","msg":"你試過笑跟住比人問你&quot;梗係好好賺喇？笑到見牙唔見眼&quot;<br />\n你仲會唔會再笑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b780fb1371c4255c993d7b597b35f80e5b50c94c","tid":112382,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:48:56.000Z","msg":"會笑咪又係經理捽出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有基本禮貌好來好去就算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人講咩開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece8616937a75f82ba9a0ee0f01bb77a5860ee85","tid":112382,"uid":83380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:03:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會笑咪又係經理捽出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有基本禮貌好來好去就算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人講咩開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地連基本禮貌都冇"},{"pid":"2a7020a48fc960638336b866d50cbb00d0b8eb6b","tid":112382,"uid":83380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:07:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>望住你笑既都係有陰謀架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔笑都到少俾d禮貌，又唔係我想咁多野問佢係上面規定送藥一定要問佢攞</blockquote><br />\n唔笑又唔代表無禮貌<br />\n你又諗下上面規定要問，佢返咁耐工聽過幾多次？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔笑都算啦，又冇禮貌，問佢野好似阻住佢咁。<br />\n<br />\n而且呢個程序係受權黎，係佢地專業一部份，工作一部份。何況我夠問過佢好多次啦得佢覺得煩咩？"},{"pid":"c11ba9d13b4111229acb012a1888fc2d6bfa0ea8","tid":112382,"uid":2781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:10:37.000Z","msg":"香港係中國領土點笑得出"},{"pid":"62bc1afea2ae8594f5bc1c5ea584f59911cad0f3","tid":112382,"uid":48285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/20sr5kme\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F20sr5kme&h=3e7ada4f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e247d33bbb2158630c4ffa3aa3f32f044f993a6","tid":112382,"uid":72647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:25:00.000Z","msg":"我認真做野，笑乜撚野。<br />\non9要求"},{"pid":"b2b930f9a63a42c7e56ae839c85434ea1bba0b86","tid":112382,"uid":79056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:46:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>望住你笑既都係有陰謀架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔笑都到少俾d禮貌，又唔係我想咁多野問佢係上面規定送藥一定要問佢攞</blockquote><br />\n唔笑又唔代表無禮貌<br />\n你又諗下上面規定要問，佢返咁耐工聽過幾多次？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔笑都算啦，又冇禮貌，問佢野好似阻住佢咁。<br />\n<br />\n而且呢個程序係受權黎，係佢地專業一部份，工作一部份。何況我夠問過佢好多次啦得佢覺得煩咩？</blockquote><br />\n到你正式出黎做野就會明點解無笑容 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你問佢答＝正常程序，三唔識七真係唔知笑乜鳩<br />\n職場會對住你笑嗰D人要多加提防呀巴打"},{"pid":"68c762cf0a650952aaaa945213b7eaf1e3d0b975","tid":112382,"uid":83380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:47:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港係中國領土點笑得出</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你岩"},{"pid":"ca4afd4a8b8ab4e1912091b38051134b8b75a322","tid":112382,"uid":83380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:49:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n唔笑又唔代表無禮貌<br />\n你又諗下上面規定要問，佢返咁耐工聽過幾多次？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔笑都算啦，又冇禮貌，問佢野好似阻住佢咁。<br />\n<br />\n而且呢個程序係受權黎，係佢地專業一部份，工作一部份。何況我夠問過佢好多次啦得佢覺得煩咩？</blockquote><br />\n到你正式出黎做野就會明點解無笑容 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你問佢答＝正常程序，三唔識七真係唔知笑乜鳩<br />\n職場會對住你笑嗰D人要多加提防呀巴打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔笑唔係我最介意，介意既係佢地冇禮貌十問9唔應，問佢野仲好似阻住佢咁。"},{"pid":"16d44196b8ded50cb354bcbe872ce60b96c6c5e7","tid":112382,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:54:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06ab09774196270b2aff6312d0cb36c547914813","tid":112382,"uid":623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:16:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人地藥劑師你叫人師傅緊係黑你面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問該如果稱呼？</blockquote><br />\n「唔該 有冇a10 xxx份藥」就得<br />\n<br />\n&quot;師傅&quot;真係笑撚死 好似地盤or的士狗</blockquote><br />\n叫都叫返阿sir 啦。 叫師傅我聽到都黑你面"},{"pid":"11ac4e979e31b1821e68f188515ad021b50af5b9","tid":112382,"uid":83380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:27:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人地藥劑師你叫人師傅緊係黑你面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問該如果稱呼？</blockquote><br />\n「唔該 有冇a10 xxx份藥」就得<br />\n<br />\n&quot;師傅&quot;真係笑撚死 好似地盤or的士狗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下次我會留意下"},{"pid":"02e826be082c2dc54182b0c669e86529a184f9b0","tid":112382,"uid":51924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:38:30.000Z","msg":"上面講個堆職業大部份搵埋都唔夠自己食 養妻活兒買樓盡孝道全部要下世做 你笑比我睇下"}]}